info.description:
pygce

A tool to export, save, and analyze your  Garmin Connect data.

Install

- $ python3 setup.py (install from source)

Questions and issues

The github issue tracker is only for bug reports and feature requests.    Anything else, such as questions for help in using the tool, should be posted in StackOverflow.
